MkCommand - Class in br.com.eits.m4j.bean

is possible to send a command with parameters more easily by using
the aiding methods
MkCommand(String) - Constructor for class br.com.eits.m4j.bean.MkCommand
The base command to send for the router For example: To retrieve the ip address list send: /ip/address/print as base command if you want to put any parameter in this command, use the MkCommand.appendParameter(String, String) method
